{"tid":1677112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"300食肆受累結業 張宇人料倒閉潮持續","createTime":"2019-10-27T01:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T09:52:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"35aa045ff90f304ec8e912fb7a493270da8ef3ea","tid":1677112,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】受反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威拖累，立法會飲食界議員張宇人今日指出，本港已有200至300間食肆受影響而結業，預料倒閉潮會持續。<br />\n<br />\n身兼行政會議成員的張宇人早上出席電台節目時表示，飲食業面對的艱難情況，較諸2003年爆發沙士疫情時更差。若示威情況持續，估計或有逾千間食肆結業。他又認為，示威者因政見不同而針對破壞某些集團的店鋪，最終令員工受影響。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人表示，已向財政司司長陳茂波反映業界面對的問題，希望政府盡快全數100%擔保業界貸款，令僱主可以給員工「出糧」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BTy5JiAPvBLBUhQRxt0dYQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191026a105646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBTy5JiAPvBLBUhQRxt0dYQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191026a105646.jpg&h=e591b09d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-300%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%8F%97%E7%B4%AF%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AE%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%99%E5%80%92%E9%96%89%E6%BD%AE%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-025500811.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-300%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25AE%2587%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%2580%2592%25E9%2596%2589%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C-025500811.html&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uORTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6cc7a7ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-300%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E5%8F%97%E7%B4%AF%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AE%87%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%